== fxsig ==

A script to be notifed of forex signal

= Help =

python fxsig.py --help


= Changes =

version 0.3
 - fix issue 1
 - fix problems when notifier's handlers are not installed
 - notifications contains images with Mac or Linux
 - added a option to parametrized the check delay for signal (default 30 seconds)
 - randomize the signal connection period
 - check every 25 seconds current prices
